1. 下载

    官网:

        https://httpd.apache.org/

    软件列表:

	httpd-2.4.53.tar.bz2
        apr-1.7.0.tar.bz2
	apr-util-1.6.1.tar.bz2
	apr-iconv-1.2.2.tar.bz2

2. 安装

    依赖库
        
        libpcre3
        
        libpcre3-dev
        
        libexpat1
        
        libexpat1-dev
        
    httpd
        
        apr-1.7.0.tar.bz2 解压到 srclib/apr
        
        apr-util-1.6.1.tar.bz2 解压到 srclib/apr-util
        
        ./configure --with-included-apr
        
        make
        
        make install


3. 启动

    /usr/local/apache2/bin/apachectl -k start
